                        working: "ΔH°f(C₃H₈) = [3 × ΔH°c(C)] + [4 × ΔH°c(H₂)] − [ΔH°c(C₃H₈)]\n= [3 × (−393)] + [4 × (−286)] − [(−2220)]\n= (−1179) + (−1144) − (−2220)\n= −2323 + 2220",
