                        working: "Group 1 elements: H (Z=1), Li (Z=3), Na (Z=11), K (Z=19)... The 1st IE of 496 kJ/mol matches sodium (Na, 1st IE = 496 kJ/mol). Lithium 1st IE = 520, potassium 1st IE = 419 — Na is the match.",
                        result: "Element X is sodium (Na)."
