        create:     "Formulate a set of molecular design criteria that a pharmaceutical chemist would apply to maximise a drug's water solubility for intravenous injection. Your criteria must: (1) identify which intermolecular forces must be maximised between drug and water; (2) specify which functional groups or structural features achieve this; (3) explain the trade-off between water solubility and membrane permeability using intermolecular force arguments; and (4) give one example of a structural modification that increases water solubility and explain its mechanism."
