        create:     "Construct a logical argument — from three independent lines of evidence — that demonstrates benzene cannot be represented as cyclohexatriene (Kekulé structure) and must instead have a delocalised π system. For each piece of evidence: state the observation or data; state what the Kekulé structure predicts; explain the discrepancy; and state what the delocalised model predicts instead. Conclude by calculating the delocalisation energy from the thermochemical data above."
