        "ΔG = ΔG° for all conditions — FALSE: ΔG° applies only at standard conditions (298 K, 1 mol dm⁻³, 100 kPa); ΔG = ΔG° + RT ln Q for non-standard conditions, where Q is the reaction quotient. At equilibrium Q = K and ΔG = 0"
